description: This file defines a single exported function 'render' that generates HTML content for the Basic Settings page, including a form for user profile details. It focuses on rendering UI components and uses internationalization for the title and subtitle.

methods.name: render(container, i18n = { t: (s) => s })
methods.description: Renders the Basic Settings page inside a specified container, displaying a header, subtitle, form with input fields for display name and email, and action buttons. Supports internationalization for textual content.
